data.description: PRICE REDUCED! Seller is very motivated. Rare Opportunity in a very desirable area on a corner lot & nestled in a quiet cul-de-sac. This convenient location is close to parks, schools, restaurants, & shopping. As you enter the living room the vaulted ceilings & great room concept feels spacious & open. The fireplace is perfect for those chilly evenings & is a cozy focal point. There is plenty of space in the living room for formal dining for  family meals or entertaining.  One of the best features about this home is that it has 2 delightful patios located off the kitchen which adds so much natural light and makes the kitchen feel huge. The larger patio has a covered area perfect for year-round outside dining.  Plenty of space for your BBQ! As you walk out from the covered patio to the sunny side yard which could be ideal for a garden area.   A blank canvas for your own creative ideas & vision. The smaller patio is shady and cozy and a nice place to read and have your morning coffee. This home has a well thought out floor plan with 2 large bedrooms and 2 full bathrooms, ample closets, cabinets, and storage areas. The vaulted ceilings make it appear much larger than it really is. Priced to sell, this home is just waiting for you to add your special touches & make it your own!!
